    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, so you're saying the disagreement is just a \"refusal to acknowledge\" things? that feels pretty biased. if scientists are actually debating the long-term physical impacts of these treatments, isn't that a legitimate scientific debate rather than just people being \"unwilling\" to see the truth?",
